    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to small objects, of any shape or material, pierced so that they may be strung or hung or attached, as by sewing.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
